2... g6 { We continue with our plan } 3. Bb2 Nf6
{ This is the key move. Black is not afraid of the doubled pawns after Bxf6, and we also invite e5. }
4. e5 Nd5 5. Qf3 { Preferred move by a Russian GM, Alexander Morozevich. } 5...
Nb4 { I like this aggressive move. } 6. Na3
