6... Nc6
{ I prefer this way to attack White's center but give  6...Bg4!?  is a nice alternative. }
7. Be3 Bg4 8. d5 Bxf3 9. Bxf3 Ne5 10. Be2 { allows a nice tactic } 10... Nxc4
11. Bxc4 Bxc3+ 12. Kf1
{ 12.bxc3  Qxc3+  13.Bd2  Qxc4∓  is close to winning for Black. } 12... Bg7
{ Black has a healthy pawn with minimal compensation for White } *

