10. Ba2
{ 10.Bb5+  Bd7∓  Black is ready to trade pieces, castle queenside and convert the material advantage. }
10... Bg4 { It's always nice to develop with a tempo! } 11. Qg5 Rg8
{ 11...Bf6  is also strong. } 12. Be3
{ 12.Bd2  stops our threat but Black is much better after  12...Qd7  13.f3  h6  14.Qh4  Bf6!  15.Qxh6  Bxf3!  16.Nxf3  Nxf3+  17.gxf3  Rg1  crushing! }
12... Nf3+ { The point of our last move Rg8 is revealed. } 13. Nxf3 Bxc3+ 14.
bxc3 Rxg5 15. Nxg5 f6 { Game over, Black is just winning here. } *

