8. Be2 Nc6 9. O-O e6 10. h3 Bxf3 11. Bxf3 Nge7
{ Black has a comfortable position. The plan is to play ...Nf5 and target the d4 pawn. Later, we can also play ...f6 to activate the g7 bishop. }
