Kxg7 20. Qxb4 Rb8
{ See the theory up to this point in the chapter. I played out this position against the weakened Leela engine with only 500 milliseconds per move. }
21. Qc3 Kg8
{ Black gets out of discovered check and ready to start his play on the queenside }
22. g4 { 22.Nc6  Bxc6  23.dxc6  Ra8  with counterplay on the a-file } 22...
hxg4 23. fxg4 Rb7
