{ This is the move order from my course @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/pp1ppppp/8/2p5/4P3/5N2/PPPP1PPP/RNBQKB1R b KQkq - 1 2@@EndFEN@@  2...g6  3.d4  cxd4  4.Nxd4  Nf6  5.Nc3  Nc6  6.Be3  Bg7  . }
